# Web-only devshell — Node + pnpm, no Rust toolchain.
# Activates when you `cd web/rmk-editor`.
#
# Reads the ROOT flake two levels up (../../flake.nix: web/rmk-editor →
# kobu). No per-subdirectory flake exists — kobu has exactly one source of
# truth at the repo root. `watch_file` reloads this shell whenever the root
# flake or its lockfile changes, so bumping Node at the root invalidates
# this cache too.
watch_file ../../flake.nix ../../flake.lock
use flake "path:../..#web"
